title: Bittersweet Distractions part 3. The Foreign Legion 2001-2005
description:
Bittersweet Distractors

Q: What is Bittersweet Distractors ?
A: A compilation of the essential Non-Album Tracks of Radiohead. On Discs 1-3 you can find the B Sides in a well flowing order and on Discs 4-6 amzaing performed and recorded Live Tracks. High-resolution artworks are to be found in the packages too.
